name: Cargo Syndrome
description: You are a UAC special ops solider stationed in the European interdimensional station, monitoring the area when it happens. Bam, like a gunshot. Project torus has made progress, except the scientists aren't very... Great with containing the specimen for experimentation, so the demons pour in greater numbers. Needless to say, there were numerous causalities. Now it's your job to secure and contain project torus and shut off it's power grid, even if it means destroying the facility. You're not gonna let these bastards win. Not now, not ever.
